title: Finding Our Voices with Samara Bay
itunes:title: Finding Our Voices with Samara Bay
description:
Dialect coach and host of the podcast of Permission to Speak Samara Bay shares her insights around language, policing women's vocal patterns and how to trust your voice.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
